{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解圆屏衍射和圆孔衍射现象。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">入射光的波长大于障碍物尺寸或与障碍物尺寸相差不多时能观察到明显的衍射现象。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">菲涅尔衍射实验仪</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">.观察圆屏衍射图像；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">移动摄像机位置，观察衍射图像变化；</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">改变圆屏半径，观察衍射图像变化；</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">观察圆孔衍射；</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">移动摄像机位置，观察衍射图像变化；</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">6.<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">改变圆孔半径，观察衍射图像变化；</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">圆屏衍射与圆孔衍射都是光的波动性的体现，半径越小，衍射现象越明显。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}